                        <p class="body-large">By tackling this issue in DataTile we can easily set up the minimum group size for which the data is displayed.</p>
                        <p class="body-large">This is even more important for huge international companies, where you need to cope also with multilanguage surveys and databases. The main goal is to provide both a general overview and detailed analytics easily and understandably to the final users, who have no time and desire to deep dive into the new tool. This is the way we solved the task for <a href="/cases/transformed-employee-satisfaction-analysis" target="_blank"><span class="link-text">the building materials manufacturer</span></a>.</p>
